env PAGER=cat man timing_path_based_enable_report_launch_clock_pat h
Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
timing_path_b...nch_clock_path(25.10)    timing_path_b...nch_clock_path(25.10)

Name
       timing_path_based_enable_report_launch_clock_path

Syntax
       timing_path_based_enable_report_launch_clock_path {true | false}

       Default: true

       Allows  the  reporting  launch  clock path in path-based analysis (PBA)
       path type full report.

       When set to false, the software does not report these paths in the tim-
       ing reports.

       To set this global variable, use the set command.

